{"tid":113680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(毒撚買衫系列)網上購物要小心","createTime":"2017-02-09T07:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T07:54:39.000Z","uid":78598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"736b7b9e69a2092ef7b129a19bc867c271f69482","tid":113680,"uid":78598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T07:35:06.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n小弟是一條大毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n毒撚冇野做就係上FB幻想自己有好多野做<br />\n<br />\n係上FB 期間  見到有個賣衫page好似好型<br />\n由於當時臨近新年  <br />\n我當然想黎一個大改造變型男 <br />\n等表哥可以唔再打我 表姐對我流哂西水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以就click左入去佢個網頁睇<br />\n<br />\n由於我成日覺得d mk仔著軍褸著到好型<br />\n所以就即刻買左件軍褸($480)諗住新年可以著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新年過去  貨未送到  <br />\n當然  表哥繼續打我 表姐又笑鳩我柒都算<br />\n不過都唔緊要 我有信心下年新年型返！<br />\n<br />\n樂觀完 崔佢出貨 <br />\n今日見到件褸就知道我下年命運係唔會變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢話唔多講 有圖有真相<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/to8wjyxi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fto8wjyxi&h=25eada1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咦  就咁睇好似都ok喎  係質地差左少少<br />\n但480蚊算係咁啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hp0fivge\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhp0fivge&h=34b2d27b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n件褸下面有個收腰橡筋位  唔錯喎  幾貼心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉一拉 成條拉左出黎  而家吊吊fing係度好似恥笑緊我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/psx8qr0o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpsx8qr0o&h=c4786f1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n心口有d英文字   毒撚我英文差<br />\n有冇人可以話我知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/r9jkhzf2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fr9jkhzf2&h=dc326903&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n背後都有d英文字  除左money 同埋time 其他字都唔知咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實除左呢件褸  我仲買左條褲<br />\n都遇到差唔多既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個故事教訓左我  毒撚千祈唔好諗住扮型<br />\n如果唔係就好似我咁  俾錢買柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n網店個名叫inlab  有興趣可以上去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ec433e39dd759d2eb81678e81000fe3946ab5c","tid":113680,"uid":20943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T07:42:39.000Z","msg":"上fb/ig買衫全部都係on9"},{"pid":"fc310dc601e8a75b1831e166ed1f42c8d4f79029","tid":113680,"uid":52839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T07:44:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上fb/ig買衫全部都係on9</blockquote><br />\n九成淘寶野"},{"pid":"836d7bfbc584cc6decf63ffd1b5b90fc919dfcee","tid":113680,"uid":78598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T07:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上fb/ig買衫全部都係on9</blockquote><br />\n九成淘寶野</blockquote><br />\n冇錯   所以我下次直接淘寶算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdad3aaec985d970ec79cb08dce7c7f886b13259","tid":113680,"uid":61586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T07:49:46.000Z","msg":"巴打,男裝唔好貪平上網買<br />\n一定要試清楚!<br />\n毒撚型左就唔再係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n猶記得當年我都好毒,著女人街貨,牛仔褲洗完又洗<br />\n<br />\n然後自己搵到錢忍住唔買野,去朱古力柒到拍住個公仔同個SALES講「一套丫唔該」<br />\n<br />\n然後學人著潮牌。<br />\n<br />\n要脫毒！眼光行先！買衫行後！<br />\n最重要乾淨整齊！"},{"pid":"fb72399884c516df52c7b834a87945cbcd88f965","tid":113680,"uid":78598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T07:54:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打,男裝唔好貪平上網買<br />\n一定要試清楚!<br />\n毒撚型左就唔再係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n猶記得當年我都好毒,著女人街貨,牛仔褲洗完又洗<br />\n<br />\n然後自己搵到錢忍住唔買野,去朱古力柒到拍住個公仔同個SALES講「一套丫唔該」<br />\n<br />\n然後學人著潮牌。<br />\n<br />\n要脫毒！眼光行先！買衫行後！<br />\n最重要乾淨整齊！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n爸打你好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n慘在我冇乜眼光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}